{"id":85593,"date":[{"year":1946,"month":2,"day":22}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"世纪风","column":"","genre":"","count":"208","ytitle":"","mtitle":"我的恐怖","ftitle":"","authors":["方平"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"方平"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"读文汇报十三日社论十四日施复亮函但见处处为‘天窗’所开，愤而有作。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有一点声音"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有一点颜色"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"慈和的白"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"安详的静"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但是，我的眼光一触到他"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我怕呀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的神经震慄呀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就像看到了一群群阴险的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肺结核菌所吞噬成的一个个的空洞；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有一点声音!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但是这里窒息住了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千千万万人的心底的呼声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有一点颜色!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但是这底下掩去了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千千万万件血写的事实。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"慈和的白!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我怕呀，但是，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"安详的静!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的神经震慄呀，但是，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天下太平!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我悲哀得快要发狂了呀，但是!"}]}